    <div class="section__sub-section">
      <p class="section__sub-header">Building Inspection</p>
      <p class="section_item">
      Once you finish buildout, a building inspector will come out to inspect your space before they will allow you to open. This can take significant time, because it’s rare to pass inspection the first time.
      Buildout will almost certainly take you longer than you planned, so make sure you add a few extra weeks into your timeline beyond what you think it will take.
      </p>
